the best type of microphone to use which will ensure all participants will be heard?

QUESTION NO: 5
Which three actions should you take if you are setting up a room to be optimal for the use of
Telepresence technology? (Choose three.)
A. Avoid noisy backgrounds
B. Preset camera positions
C. Cover up the camera
D. Keep the doors open
E. Close the curtains or blinds to eliminate natural light
F. Turn off the light
G. Open the curtains or blinds to gain natural light.
Answer: A,B,E
Explanation:
